{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps [LAUGHS] in a negative way, in the fact that we were picked on by Hitler and the Nazis, and that we became subject to various laws, although we didn't have too much of it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we, we saw the stormtroopers, and the fact that they didn't like Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously, my parents made us aware of the fact that Hitler, who came to power in 1933-- so after that time, it became fairly clear that the regime didn't like Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to say that it didn't affect me at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I carried on in school-- in, in this state school, where I was perhaps the only Jew in the class or maybe one of the few Jews in the whole school kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't remember ever having been picked on or beaten or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that way, I don't think it affected me at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But obviously, it affected my parents kind of thing, because they could understand what was happening-- the more and more things you were not allowed to do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously, my father's job would be-- might be in jeopardy in the future.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And more and more Jews were emigrating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For example, the uncle and aunt who visited us in Berlin, they both emigrated in 1933 kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My aunt went to Palestine, and the uncle went to London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they, obviously, could see that life was not good in Berlin, and, and there was no future for Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I, I, I just don't remember anything about those sort of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have learned recently now talking about it and all these sort of things, that we didn't talk much with our parents at all.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
